    "The model is licensed for commercial use.",
    "Kauf et al. [29] adopted MPT and other LLMs to investigate the dynamics of agent-patient interactions.",
    "In addition to the base MPT-7B, other three models were released including MPT-7B-Instruct, MPT-7B-Chat, and MPT-7B-StoryWriter-65k+.",
    "July 2023 In July 2023, in partnership with Microsoft, Meta introduced a series of models under the name LLaMa 2, boasting varying parameter sizes of 7 billion, 13 billion, and an impressive 70 billion.",
